column8: Angry Birds is a video game franchise inspired primarily by a sketch of stylized wingless birds; with two billion downloads across all platforms. Angry Birds has been praised for its successful combination of addictive gameplay; comical style; and low price.)

Chicago Fire is an American television drama series that airs on NBC. The show explores the lives; both professional and personal; of the firefighters and paramedics of the Chicago Fire Department. NBC renewed the series for a third season.)
